WEBVTT

00:03.287 --> 00:05.307
You should always try new things and challenge yourself.

00:05.787 --> 00:08.149
I think that's the fun part about fashion.

00:09.751 --> 00:11.958
There really aren't rules about what you can do.

00:12.513 --> 00:13.315
You know, day in day out.

00:13.809 --> 00:17.000
The fun part about style and your look is that you can change it.

00:17.200 --> 00:19.251
It's like an ongoing art project.

00:19.853 --> 00:20.682
Own your look.

00:20.961 --> 00:21.876
Love your style.

00:22.169 --> 00:22.940
Make a statement.

00:23.202 --> 00:24.736
There are a million ways to be brave.

